description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for Amazon EBS Provisioned Rate for Volume Initialization, which lets you specify a volume initialization rate to ensure that your EBS volumes are initialized in a predictable amount of time.

[``botocore``] ServiceCatalog's APIs (DeleteServiceAction, DisassociateServiceActionFromProvisioningArtifact, AssociateServiceActionWithProvisioningArtifact) now throw InvalidParametersException when IdempotencyToken is invalid.
[``botocore``] Add dualstack endpoints support and correct us-gov-west-1 FIPS endpoint.
